00:13:27,650 --> 00:13:29,580
You can choose to keep or remove it.

293
00:13:30,860 --> 00:13:31,630
Watch.

294
00:13:38,330 --> 00:13:40,790
You can't even tell whether it's fake or not.

295
00:13:41,570 --> 00:13:43,230
And there's no real or fake...

296
00:13:44,320 --> 00:13:45,850
because all of this is mine.

297
00:13:46,000 --> 00:13:48,000
Also, it doesn't really matter what's real,

298
00:13:48,000 --> 00:13:48,790
isn't it?

299
00:13:49,790 --> 00:13:50,480
Well,

300
00:13:50,910 --> 00:13:51,910
you two should

301
00:13:51,910 --> 00:13:53,040
cut your braids too.

302
00:13:55,270 --> 00:13:56,270
Cut it if you want.

303
00:13:56,600 --> 00:13:57,910
I won't cut it anyway.

304
00:13:58,890 --> 00:14:00,130
Me neither.

305
00:14:01,050 --> 00:14:01,900
You guys!

306
00:14:02,100 --> 00:14:02,760
Attention!

307
00:14:05,080 --> 00:14:05,720
Salute!

308
00:14:11,150 --> 00:14:11,790
Firstly,

309
00:14:12,910 --> 00:14:15,480
congratulations on completing your enlistment training.

310
00:14:15,480 --> 00:14:17,750
Thank you, Drillmaster Hirata

311
00:14:25,730 --> 00:14:26,610
Yang Kaizhi.

312
00:14:27,750 --> 00:14:29,200
You cut your hair.

313
00:14:29,670 --> 00:14:30,820
You look much better,

314
00:14:30,820 --> 00:14:31,750
don't you?

315
00:14:35,030 --> 00:14:35,720
Yes.

316
00:14:36,240 --> 00:14:37,360
I think so too.

317
00:14:38,200 --> 00:14:38,870
Of course.

318
00:14:39,790 --> 00:14:40,920
The school

319
00:14:41,240 --> 00:14:43,870
respects your cultural norms,

320
00:14:44,360 --> 00:14:45,360
and also,

321
00:14:47,300 --> 00:14:49,350
your personal choice.

322
00:14:51,870 --> 00:14:53,320
A new phase of studies

323
00:14:53,510 --> 00:14:55,150
is about to start.

324
00:14:56,120 --> 00:14:57,360
I'm not sure

325
00:14:57,840 --> 00:14:59,440
if you guys can get used to it.

326
00:15:00,200 --> 00:15:01,400
But there's one thing

327
00:15:02,000 --> 00:15:04,320
that I can be sure of.

328
00:15:04,960 --> 00:15:06,360
Your new phase of studies

329
00:15:06,510 --> 00:15:09,080
has nothing to do with

330
00:15:10,000 --> 00:15:11,480
the length of your hair.

331
00:15:21,200 --> 00:15:21,870
Dismissed.

332
00:15:26,570 --> 00:15:27,900
Hirata speaks Chinese?

333
00:15:28,480 --> 00:15:30,550
I heard he's a China Hand.

334
00:15:30,830 --> 00:15:32,390
He's also our drillmaster.

335
00:15:32,660 --> 00:15:33,760
I've checked the schedule.

336
00:15:33,760 --> 00:15:35,430
It seems like he teaches horse riding.

337
00:15:35,430 --> 00:15:36,500
Horse riding?

338
00:15:55,650 --> 00:15:56,770
Firstly,

339
00:15:57,850 --> 00:15:59,580
we must understand the horses,

340
00:16:00,790 --> 00:16:02,450
get familiar with the horses,

341
00:16:02,870 --> 00:16:04,200
get close to the horses,

342
00:16:05,030 --> 00:16:07,320
and regard it as a silent comrade.

343
00:16:09,510 --> 00:16:11,970
You should be connected to the horse by blood

344
00:16:12,480 --> 00:16:13,870
and through the heart,

345
00:16:14,630 --> 00:16:16,750
in order to empathize with each other.

346
00:16:16,750 --> 00:16:17,750
You should aspire

347
00:16:18,480 --> 00:16:20,240
to feel like there's no one on your horse,

348
00:16:20,240 --> 00:16:22,240
and to feel no horse under your hips.

349
00:16:23,150 --> 00:16:24,960
You should be one with the horse

350
00:16:25,750 --> 00:16:27,080
to be qualified to ride.

351
00:16:47,030 --> 00:16:47,910
Isn't this a sage discussing

352
00:16:47,910 --> 00:16:49,360
the Three-Character Classic?

353
00:16:49,360 --> 00:16:50,690
His horse riding skills

354
00:16:50,840 --> 00:16:52,240
is not even as good as you.

355
00:16:59,750 --> 00:17:01,110
Get on the horse.

356
00:17:15,640 --> 00:17:16,270
Kaizhi!

357
00:17:22,480 --> 00:17:23,890
Cadet Yang Kaizhi.

358
00:17:24,859 --> 00:17:26,420
You have done it.

359
00:17:26,829 --> 00:17:28,359
You have no one on your horse

360
00:17:28,790 --> 00:17:30,440
and no horse under your hips.

361
00:17:39,160 --> 00:17:40,070
Medics!

362
00:17:45,700 --> 00:17:47,550
There's an injured personnel over there.

363
00:17:47,550 --> 00:17:49,830
The horse is injured too.

364
00:17:49,980 --> 00:17:51,300
Check its front legs

365
00:17:51,740 --> 00:17:53,040
and take it back to the stable.

366
00:17:53,040 --> 00:17:53,630
Yes.

367
00:18:08,310 --> 00:18:10,040
No one else is as unlucky as you.

368
00:18:10,350 --> 00:18:11,750
Don't touch it. It hurts.

369
00:18:12,070 --> 00:18:13,200
It's the first time you got on a horse,

370
00:18:13,200 --> 00:18:14,680
and yet you managed to injure both the horse and yourself.

371
00:18:14,680 --> 00:18:16,640
They said you broke the school record

372
00:18:16,640 --> 00:18:17,550
for injuring both

373
00:18:17,550 --> 00:18:18,440
the horse and yourself

374
00:18:18,440 --> 00:18:19,680
in the shortest time.

375
00:18:19,760 --> 00:18:21,310
I've never rode a horse before.

376
00:18:21,310 --> 00:18:21,830
Even so,

377
00:18:21,830 --> 00:18:23,660
you should know how to hold the rein, right?

378
00:18:23,660 --> 00:18:26,120
You were trying to climb up without the rein.

379
00:18:26,310 --> 00:18:27,550
You're a disgrace to

380
00:18:27,550 --> 00:18:28,550
the Qing dynasty.

381
00:18:33,680 --> 00:18:34,270
Here.

382
00:18:40,110 --> 00:18:40,720
Tufang,

383
00:18:42,070 --> 00:18:43,350
what are you doing?

384
00:18:43,680 --> 00:18:45,920
Try this method of treatment from our Banner Battalion.

385
00:18:45,920 --> 00:18:47,720
The school infirmary gave me a prescription though.

386
00:18:47,720 --> 00:18:48,650
That's useless.

387
00:18:49,200 --> 00:18:50,030
This method of mine

388
00:18:50,030 --> 00:18:51,460
can allow you to walk freely by tomorrow morning

389
00:18:51,460 --> 00:18:53,120
and be completely healed in three days.

390
00:18:53,120 --> 00:18:53,990
Really?

391
00:18:54,450 --> 00:18:55,310
Lift your leg.

392
00:18:55,830 --> 00:18:56,910
Be gentle. That hurts!

393
00:18:56,910 --> 00:18:57,830
Stop talking.

394
00:19:00,210 --> 00:19:02,110
The secret recipe of our Battalion

395
00:19:02,110 --> 00:19:04,160
has been passed down for over 200 years.

396
00:19:04,160 --> 00:19:04,640
That's how

397
00:19:04,640 --> 00:19:05,880
the leg injuries of the old Taikhan Nurhachi

398
00:19:05,880 --> 00:19:07,030
were treated.

399
00:19:07,460 --> 00:19:08,770
Let's not mention what it can do

400
00:19:08,770 --> 00:19:10,430
for your tender arms and legs.

401
00:19:11,480 --> 00:19:12,510
I need to apply the herbs

402
00:19:12,510 --> 00:19:13,910
directly onto your legs.

403
00:19:14,030 --> 00:19:16,490
It's mixed with some wine, so it will feel a little cold.

404
00:19:16,490 --> 00:19:17,550
Don't! That hurts.

405
00:19:17,830 --> 00:19:18,490
That hurts!

406
00:19:19,850 --> 00:19:20,440
It hurts!

407
00:19:21,070 --> 00:19:22,480
It hurts!

408
00:19:22,500 --> 00:19:23,500
Hang in there.

409
00:19:32,190 --> 00:19:32,950
Kaizhi.

410
00:19:33,470 --> 00:19:34,720
Lie down and close your eyes.

411
00:19:34,720 --> 00:19:36,580
Don't worry about anything else.

412
00:19:37,540 --> 00:19:38,010
Slowly.

413
00:19:38,230 --> 00:19:38,760
Don't...

414
00:19:43,700 --> 00:19:45,370
That hurts!

415
00:19:46,010 --> 00:19:46,660
Renjun.

416
00:19:47,200 --> 00:19:48,740
Hold him down. Don't let him move.

417
00:19:48,740 --> 00:19:50,030
No, no, you don't have to.

418
00:19:50,030 --> 00:19:50,720
No, don't!

419
00:19:50,750 --> 00:19:52,480
You guys help me lift up his leg.

420
00:19:53,000 --> 00:19:54,200
Just close your eyes.

421
00:19:54,480 --> 00:19:54,960
You...

422
00:19:54,990 --> 00:19:55,880
Shut up.

423
00:19:56,680 --> 00:19:57,920
It's cold!

424
00:19:58,830 --> 00:19:59,720
Don't scream.

425
00:20:11,040 --> 00:20:12,150
Don't scream.

426
00:20:42,720 --> 00:20:43,780
Does it still hurt?

427
00:20:47,130 --> 00:20:48,200
It doesn't hurt,

428
00:20:49,440 --> 00:20:51,040
but it's just a little scary.

429
00:20:54,830 --> 00:20:55,680
Look at you.

430
00:20:56,010 --> 00:20:57,920
Treating the horse after treating the man.

431
00:20:57,920 --> 00:20:58,710
To be honest,

432
00:20:58,920 --> 00:21:00,380
you are really a loyal man.

433
00:21:11,170 --> 00:21:12,300
That's all?

434
00:21:13,680 --> 00:21:15,680
There's still one more ritual to go.

435
00:21:15,830 --> 00:21:17,680
We have to pray to the God of Horse.

436
00:21:17,680 --> 00:21:18,680
Pray?

437
00:21:19,400 --> 00:21:20,200
Is this another secret recipe

438
00:21:20,200 --> 00:21:21,800
from your Banner Battalion?

439
00:21:35,800 --> 00:21:37,660
The heavenly master of the steed,

440
00:21:38,640 --> 00:21:40,000
please tame and restrain

441
00:21:40,000 --> 00:21:41,200
these fierce horses,

442
00:21:41,900 --> 00:21:43,780
dispel any calamity,

443
00:21:44,310 --> 00:21:45,840
and remove any misfortune.

444
00:21:46,720 --> 00:21:49,310
Make them like to graze and drink water.

445
00:21:49,720 --> 00:21:50,720
May they carry people

446
00:21:50,720 --> 00:21:52,650
on their own without being guided.

447
00:21:53,310 --> 00:21:54,480
May they get out

448
00:21:54,640 --> 00:21:56,570
of the stable without being urged.

449
00:21:58,070 --> 00:21:59,350
Let their noses

450
00:22:00,110 --> 00:22:01,710
be able to smell fragrances.

451
00:22:02,200 --> 00:22:03,270
Let their ears

452
00:22:03,270 --> 00:22:04,550
be able to hear songs.

453
00:22:05,070 --> 00:22:06,200
Let their eyes

454
00:22:06,200 --> 00:22:08,070
be as bright as the sky.

455
00:22:08,710 --> 00:22:11,390
Let the head be the balance of the body,

456
00:22:12,720 --> 00:22:13,680
the spine

457
00:22:13,870 --> 00:22:15,660
be the core of the body,

458
00:22:16,440 --> 00:22:19,110
and the legs be the support of the body.

459
00:22:19,600 --> 00:22:22,320
Let the tail repel mosquitoes.

460
00:22:23,240 --> 00:22:24,110
Let the abdomen

461
00:22:24,510 --> 00:22:26,770
become a treasure bag of grass and herbs.

462
00:22:27,120 --> 00:22:28,920
Let them travel a thousand miles

463
00:22:29,200 --> 00:22:30,610
and gallop freely.

464
00:22:41,430 --> 00:22:42,830
What are you two doing?

465
00:22:43,820 --> 00:22:45,410
How did the horse recover?

466
00:22:47,100 --> 00:22:48,490
How did you recover too?

467
00:22:49,110 --> 00:22:51,840
You're not in pain anymore? You can get out of bed?

468
00:22:55,310 --> 00:22:56,510
I can walk now,

469
00:22:57,710 --> 00:22:59,240
but it still hurts a little.

470
00:23:01,370 --> 00:23:02,500
Don't be too greedy.

471
00:23:02,580 --> 00:23:03,440
You should have

472
00:23:03,470 --> 00:23:06,130
waited until tomorrow morning to get out of bed.

473
00:23:12,030 --> 00:23:13,430
Am I seeing incorrectly?

474
00:23:13,590 --> 00:23:14,550
Yang Kaizhi?

475
00:23:14,550 --> 00:23:15,830
It’s me, drillmaster.

476
00:23:17,030 --> 00:23:19,640
I thought you were still in the infirmary.

477
00:23:19,700 --> 00:23:20,170
No,

478
00:23:20,530 --> 00:23:21,420
I'm here.

479
00:23:23,680 --> 00:23:24,720
That's strange.

480
00:23:25,620 --> 00:23:27,220
The horse has recovered too?

481
00:23:27,270 --> 00:23:28,000
Yes.

482
00:23:28,350 --> 00:23:31,350
There's a man on the horse and a horse under the crotch.

483
00:23:38,210 --> 00:23:39,380
I heard

484
00:23:39,720 --> 00:23:41,480
you cast a spell.

485
00:23:42,270 --> 00:23:44,720
Amazing, Liang Xiang.

486
00:23:45,720 --> 00:23:46,680
Drillmaster,

487
00:23:46,790 --> 00:23:48,070
it's not a spell.

488
00:23:48,550 --> 00:23:50,900
It's the miracle of my ancestors.

489
00:23:53,810 --> 00:23:55,850
Your ancestors

490
00:23:56,020 --> 00:23:57,570
were indeed miraculous.

491
00:24:00,880 --> 00:24:02,830
But what about now?

492
00:24:43,750 --> 00:24:44,510
Tufang,

493
00:24:46,360 --> 00:24:47,290
don't be too sad.

494
00:24:48,080 --> 00:24:50,140
I'm the one that got you into trouble.

495
00:24:51,260 --> 00:24:52,440
I didn't expect Drillmaster Hirata

496
00:24:52,440 --> 00:24:53,680
would do such a thing.

497
00:24:55,440 --> 00:24:56,790
How can I not be sad?

498
00:24:57,710 --> 00:24:58,820
He's straightforward

499
00:24:58,820 --> 00:24:59,580
and honest.

500
00:25:01,550 --> 00:25:03,110
Look at the Japanese military academy.

501
00:25:03,110 --> 00:25:04,790
Even the crown prince is no exception.

502
00:25:04,790 --> 00:25:07,390
He also has to struggle on the training fields.

503
00:25:07,710 --> 00:25:08,710
But what about us?

504
00:25:18,030 --> 00:25:19,720
Your Japanese drillmaster

505
00:25:20,960 --> 00:25:23,090
talked about our ancestors like this?

506
00:25:24,050 --> 00:25:24,770
Mother,

507
00:25:26,440 --> 00:25:27,970
is there sense in his words?

508
00:25:36,830 --> 00:25:38,790
It's a bit harsh

509
00:25:39,270 --> 00:25:40,620
when others say it.

510
00:25:42,920 --> 00:25:44,160
We Manchurians

511
00:25:44,680 --> 00:25:46,320
were really smart at the top

512
00:25:47,310 --> 00:25:49,110
since the times of Khan Nurhaci,

513
00:25:49,680 --> 00:25:51,680
while the bottom was really stupid.

514
00:25:51,960 --> 00:25:52,830
So,

515
00:25:54,170 --> 00:25:55,930
that's what formed the basis

516
00:25:55,960 --> 00:25:58,090
of the Qing dynasty for over 200 years.

517
00:25:59,420 --> 00:26:01,030
The opera singers also said

518
00:26:01,550 --> 00:26:03,210
the higher-ups were too smart

519
00:26:03,440 --> 00:26:05,270
and refused to pay out.

520
00:26:06,070 --> 00:26:07,870
The lower people were smart too.

521
00:26:08,070 --> 00:26:09,800
They weren't willing to fight,

522
00:26:09,830 --> 00:26:11,360
so it was game over for them.

523
00:26:12,890 --> 00:26:13,920
What about now?

524
00:26:15,480 --> 00:26:17,440
Now, the Qing dynasty

525
00:26:17,830 --> 00:26:20,500
is also smart on both ends.

526
00:26:22,000 --> 00:26:23,880
How can we be strong?

527
00:26:28,730 --> 00:26:29,530
Son,

528
00:26:31,070 --> 00:26:32,640
don't feel wronged.

529
00:26:33,440 --> 00:26:35,550
Just let them scold you.

530
00:26:37,070 --> 00:26:38,670
If you want to rise to the top,

531
00:26:40,200 --> 00:26:41,660
you must be able to lie low.

532
00:26:43,200 --> 00:26:45,730
You must bear hardships with determination.

533
00:26:46,050 --> 00:26:47,960
You need this kind of strength.

534
00:27:03,680 --> 00:27:04,790
Duke Ayakura

535
00:27:04,850 --> 00:27:08,780
invites you and your mother to drink tea with him.

536
00:27:12,690 --> 00:27:13,210
Yes.

537
00:27:21,120 --> 00:27:23,270
Stop right ahead of that shop.

538
00:27:23,630 --> 00:27:24,630
Yes, sir.

539
00:27:23,690 --> 00:27:24,810
[Songyun Hall]

540
00:27:26,920 --> 00:27:27,550
Mother,

541
00:27:27,760 --> 00:27:28,760
I need to buy a gift

542
00:27:28,790 --> 00:27:29,920
for Duke Ayakura.

543
00:27:30,240 --> 00:27:30,960
Go ahead.

544
00:27:45,370 --> 00:27:46,740
Hello, sir.

545
00:27:46,960 --> 00:27:47,720
Hello.

546
00:27:49,550 --> 00:27:51,270
Are you Chinese?

547
00:27:52,920 --> 00:27:53,720
Yes.

548
00:27:56,720 --> 00:27:57,790
These are

549
00:27:57,790 --> 00:28:00,120
premium products customized from China.

550
00:28:00,200 --> 00:28:01,600
These are the most famous

551
00:28:01,960 --> 00:28:02,890
Huzhou brushes,

552
00:28:03,550 --> 00:28:04,680
Duanzhou inkstones,

553
00:28:04,680 --> 00:28:05,440
Huizhou ink,

554
00:28:05,600 --> 00:28:06,730
and Xuanzhou paper.

555
00:28:07,070 --> 00:28:08,270
Which would you like?

556
00:28:26,650 --> 00:28:27,910
This painting is good.

557
00:28:28,400 --> 00:28:29,800
It's just a little small.

558
00:28:30,300 --> 00:28:31,860
Is there a bigger one

559
00:28:32,240 --> 00:28:33,900
that can cover an entire wall?

560
00:28:33,970 --> 00:28:35,210
Of course.

561
00:28:36,200 --> 00:28:37,400
You can customize it.

562
00:28:37,860 --> 00:28:40,310
It'll be painted according to your requirements.

563
00:28:40,310 --> 00:28:41,440
This is pretty good.

564
00:28:42,880 --> 00:28:45,190
You can add some grapes.

565
00:28:45,320 --> 00:28:46,640
Have them all in blobs.

566
00:28:48,710 --> 00:28:50,030
Blobs?

567
00:28:51,030 --> 00:28:51,920
In my hometown,

568
00:28:52,070 --> 00:28:53,160
wisteria and grapes

569
00:28:53,160 --> 00:28:54,930
are on the same trellises year-round.

570
00:28:54,930 --> 00:28:56,990
The purple flowers and purple grapes

571
00:28:57,140 --> 00:28:58,030
are not only pleasing to the eye,

572
00:28:58,030 --> 00:28:59,890
but also delightful to the heart.

573
00:29:00,460 --> 00:29:01,860
Delightful to the heart.

574
00:29:02,720 --> 00:29:04,320
Why isn't that girl back yet?

575
00:29:05,220 --> 00:29:05,870
She went to get

576
00:29:05,870 --> 00:29:08,200
Mr. Shoushan's landscape painting.

577
00:29:08,620 --> 00:29:09,410
I see.

578
00:29:12,200 --> 00:29:13,400
Please wait a moment.

579
00:29:21,600 --> 00:29:22,360
Please.

580
00:29:33,320 --> 00:29:34,880
It's grapes, right?

581
00:29:50,280 --> 00:29:51,280
Yes.

582
00:29:51,460 --> 00:29:52,940
I see.

